      "date": "2013-05-10 06:19:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/afd87f56-b936-11e2-875f-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
